## Bayit Dashboard Tor config — Canadian exit nodes only
## Usage: tor -f scripts/torrc.bayit

SocksPort 9150
DataDirectory /tmp/tor-bayit

## Restrict exit nodes to Canada ({ca})
## Ideally BC, but Tor doesn't support province-level filtering.
## {ca} = all Canadian exit nodes.
ExitNodes {ca}
StrictNodes 1

## Performance tuning for data scraping
CircuitBuildTimeout 30
LearnCircuitBuildTimeout 0
NumEntryGuards 3
